<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Trebuchet MS,Geneva; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" align="left"><span>Get involved to help clean up your </span><span>community! Come out and volunteer with neighbors, friends and local businesses pick up trash in Madison. All necessary items will be provided, including gloves garbage bags and claws.</span></p>
