<p style="text-align: left; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Trebuchet MS,Geneva; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);" align="left"><span>Children and adults are welcome, and Rocket City Sitters will be providing free childcare at Horizon Elementary for those too young to participate (infant to age 11).&nbsp;</span></p>
